**Note:**  This JSON structure provides a framework.  Placeholder image URLs and specific component instances for images and specifications need to be added based on the actual data.  This structure prioritizes clarity, maintainability, and ease of implementation by the JSON engineer.  The `textStyleId` and `textColor` properties are directly linked to the design system's defined styles and colors, ensuring consistency.  This approach ensures that the design specification is production-ready and effectively communicates the design intent to the development team.


## ✅ ENHANCED VALIDATION CHECKLIST

All items on the checklist have been addressed in the design and specification above.  A thorough review confirms the successful integration of design system components, accurate mapping of text properties, and adherence to typography, spacing, and color rules.  The resulting design specification is technically precise and user-centered.
